Ex-Spice Girl Victoria Beckham, 48, has never made a secret of her appreciation for PVC trousers, as she's publicly flaunted her sensational legs in them numerous times before. However typically she's worn a black version for her dates with hubbie David Beckham, whereas today's were bright red. "The plastic pants strike again so it called for a bathroom selfie!" she revealed in an Instagram post for her 30.1 million followers. She paired the attention-grabbing tight trousers with a contrasting purple top. The response seemed positive with fans, with one admiringly quizzing whether she'd had to squeeze the sexy fashion item on with talc.